1. *Kosa* mi je danas jako zamršena. (My *hair* is very tangled today.)
2. *Kose* na njoj su bile dugačke i crne. (The *hairs* on her were long and black.)
3. Ona *kosi* travu u vrtu. (She is *cutting* the grass in the garden.)
4. *Kosu* treba češljati nakon pranja. (You need to comb your *hair* after washing it.)
5. Zlatna *kosa* mu je padala na ramena. (His golden *hair* was falling on his shoulders.)
6. *Kose* su joj svilenkaste i sjajne. (Her *hairs* are silky and shiny.)
7. On voli da *kosi* travu svakog vikenda. (He likes to *mow* the lawn every weekend.)
8. Ona je vezala kosu u rep. (*She tied her hair* into a ponytail.)
9. Njena *kosa* je bila isprepletana cvećem. (Her *hair* was interwoven with flowers.)
10. Ja ću ti *kositi* travu ako mi pozajmiš tvoj trimer. (I will *mow* the grass for you if you lend me your trimmer.)